'''Ignacio Jose Urrutia''' was a [[Cubans|Cuban]] [[historian]]. He was born in 1730, died 1795. His most famous work, ''Teatro historico, juridico y politico-militar de la isla Fernandina de Cuba'', was published in 1789.

